lead_paragraph: James Harden had 38 points and 10 assists for his seventh consecutive double-double, and the Houston Rockets beat the Portland Trail Blazers 130-114 on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Harden Has 38 in Rockets' 130-114 Win Over the Blazers
